  <scopecontent id="aspace_0a934112609a423bf85aa155ae018c17">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Session records; minutes; lists of marriages, baptisms, and members; minutes, accounts, and correspondence of women's organizations, including the Woman's Foreign Missionary Society and the Torrey Circle of Kings Daughters; historical data; guestbook; correspondence pertaining to early pastors, especially Joshua Leonard; receipts, checkbooks, and treasurer's reports; and other records of the Cazenovia First Presbyterian Church.</p>  </scopecontent>
